listing_info.name: Facebook Catalogue
listing_info.tagline: Export products in Facebook compatible format

benefits.title: Catalogue Export
benefits.description: Export catalogue in a format that is fully compatible to be readily used on Facebook Commerce Manager.

details.description:
Your catalogue on Fynd Platform is readily usable on Facebook Commerce Manager. This app helps you transform your Fynd Platform catalogue into Facebook's import products CSV file format without much manual intervention. You may use this exported CSV file readily on Facebook Commerce Manager to upload your products to Facebook Marketplace.

Features

  • Catalogue Export
    • Export catalogue in a format that is fully compatible to be readily used on Facebook Commerce Manager.
    • Filter the catalogue based on 'brands' to be exported. You can select multiple brands at once.
    • Get the count of products that will be exported after applying filters.
  • Scheduled Catalogue Export
    • Set a recurring event to export the catalogue. For example- every 4 hours, every day, every Friday, etc.
    • Get a constant URL that will have the latest catalogue data. You may use this URL in your system to always fetch fresh catalogue data.
  • Download History
    • A list of all the export events in past will be available. You can download the catalogue from the past export events as well.

Upcoming Features

  • Catalogue Import
    • Upload your catalogue present on the Facebook marketplace to Fynd Platform using the exported CSV from Facebook Commerce Manager.
